      <title>特朗普选择万斯加剧与外交政策保守派的分歧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-16/trump-picking-vance-widens-rift-with-old-guard-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前总统唐纳德·特朗普选择 JD Vance 作为竞选搭档，这标志着他与共和党外交政策老派彻底决裂。彭博新闻社的约翰与约翰·纳尼就“中东和非洲视野”进行了讨论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-16/trump-picking-vance-widens-rift-with-old-guard-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 08:55:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙阿：如果美联储把握好时机，软着陆就有可能实现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-16/soft-landing-possible-if-fed-gets-its-timing-right-shah-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Principal Asset Management 的 Seema Shah 表示，如果美联储从 9 月开始逐步降息，美国可能会实现“独角兽”软着陆。她在彭博电视上表示，在这种情况下，“风险资产可能会表现相当不错”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-16/soft-landing-possible-if-fed-gets-its-timing-right-shah-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 08:28:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
